  "description": "<section id=\"description\">\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">After that</span> često se koristi da pokaže šta sledi u nizu radnji ili događaja. Na primer:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">I check my emails, and after that, I attend a meeting.</span> - To znači da je prisustvovanje sastanku sledeća stvar koju radite nakon proveravanja e-pošte.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">We have a team briefing first thing in the morning, and after that, we start our individual tasks.</span> - Ovde, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">first</span> i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">after</span> pomažu u razumevanju niza događaja.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>",
